import React, { useContext, useEffect, useState } from 'react' import mycontext from './Context/Createcontext' function Selectdata() { const {Note, Getnotes}=useContext(mycontext) const [data,setData]=useState(); const [end,setEnd]=useState({EndM:0,Eyear:0}); //Call Use Effect Hook To refresh The Data useEffect(()=>{ Getnotes() },[]) const StartChange=(e)=>{ setData(e.target.value) }; console.log("Start",data) const EndChange=(e)=>{setEnd(e.target.name=e.target.value)} console.log("End",end) return (
) } export default Selectdata
